        <updateDate>2021-06-21T18:10:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Leasing Relief for Dependents of Fallen Heroes and Injured Servicemembers Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill allows an adult dependent or certain other specified representatives of a service member who was killed or catastrophically injured in military service to terminate the service member's lease of a premises or of a motor vehicle without financial penalty.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
